OL,3,CPost Office apology 'like a kick in
OL,4,Cthe teeth'
OL,6,FA former postmistress from Co Tyrone
OL,7,Fhas described an apology from the Post
OL,8,FOffice for the Horizon IT scandal as
OL,9,Flike a "kick in the teeth".
OL,11,FDeirdre Connolly was reacting
OL,12,Ffollowing today's publication of the
OL,13,Ffirst report from the Post Office
OL,14,FInquiry, which set out for the first
OL,15,Ftime the scale of suffering caused by
OL,16,Fthe faulty accounting system.
OL,18,FHundreds of postmistresses and
OL,19,Fpostmasters were wrongly accused of
OL,20,Ftheft and fraud, which drove some to
OL,21,Ftake their own lives.
