OL,3,CPost Office apology 'like a kick in
OL,4,Cthe teeth'
OL,6,FThe first tranche of the public
OL,7,Finquiry's final report concluded that
OL,8,FPost Office bosses should have known
OL,9,FHorizon was faulty but "maintained the
OL,10,Ffiction that its data was always
OL,11,Faccurate" when prosecuting
OL,12,Fsubpostmasters.
OL,14,FChairman Sir Wyn Williams said "a
OL,15,Fnumber of senior" people at the
OL,16,Forganisation were aware the system,
OL,17,Fknown as Legacy Horizon, was capable
OL,18,Fof error up until it was changed in
OL,19,F2010, with a number of employees also
OL,20,Faware the updated system, Horizon
OL,21,FOnline, also had bugs and defects.
