OL,6,FA total of 59 victims of the Horizon
OL,7,Fscandal contemplated suicide with 10
OL,8,Fattempting to take their own lives,
OL,9,FSir Wyn's final report concluded.
OL,11,FHe said there was a "real possibility"
OL,12,F13 people took their own lives as a
OL,13,Fresult of the suffering they endured
OL,14,Fduring the scandal.
OL,16,FSir Wyn said around 10,000 people are
OL,17,Feligible to submit compensation claims
OL,18,Ffollowing what has been dubbed as the
OL,19,Fworst miscarriage of justice in
OL,20,FBritish legal history.
