OL,6,FLead campaigner and former
OL,7,Fsubpostmistress Jo Hamilton said the
OL,8,Freport "shows the full scale of the
OL,9,Fhorror that they unleashed on us".
OL,11,FThe scandal was propelled into the
OL,12,Fspotlight in January last year
OL,13,Ffollowing the airing of ITV's drama Mr
OL,14,FBates Vs The Post Office, starring
OL,15,Factor Toby Jones about Sir Alan Bates,
OL,16,Fformer sub-postmaster and founder of
OL,17,Fthe Justice for Subpostmasters
OL,18,FAlliance.
