OL,3,CPost Office apology 'like a kick in
OL,4,Cthe teeth'
OL,6,FEx-Post Office chief executive Paula
OL,7,FVennells is accused of overseeing a
OL,8,Fhuge number of wrongful prosecutions
OL,9,Fand convictions, and was in post at
OL,10,Fthe time Sir Wyn said bosses should
OL,11,Fhave known Horizon was faulty.
OL,13,FThe chairman's 162-page report
OL,14,Fcriticised the "unnecessarily
OL,15,Fadversarial attitude" of the Post
OL,16,FOffice and its advisers towards making
OL,17,Fcompensation offers to victims and
OL,18,Fthat the organisation and the
OL,19,FGovernment "simply failed to grasp how
OL,20,Fdifficult it would be to provide
OL,21,Fappropriate financial redress."
