OL,6,FApproximately 1,000 people were
OL,7,Fwrongly prosecuted and convicted
OL,8,Fthroughout the UK between 1999 and
OL,9,F2015 as a result of faulty Fujitsu
OL,10,Fsoftware, with a significant number
OL,11,Fcontemplating self-harm, the report
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FSir Wyn also singled out the behaviour
OL,15,Fof Post Office investigators, saying
OL,16,Fsubpostmasters "will have been in
OL,17,Fwholly unfamiliar territory and they
OL,18,Fwill have found the experience to be
OL,19,Ftroubling at best and harrowing at
OL,20,Fworst".
