OL,6,FThe publication of the first tranche
OL,7,Fof the report on Tuesday focused
OL,8,Fsolely on the devastating impact of
OL,9,Fthe scandal on victims and the
OL,10,Fcompensation offered to
OL,11,Fsubpostmasters, with a further report
OL,12,Fpotentially attributing blame expected
OL,13,Fat a later date.
