OL,6,FTeasing his conclusions for the final
OL,7,Foverarching report, which is still
OL,8,Flikely to be some months away, Sir Wyn
OL,9,Fsaid: "Although many of the
OL,10,Findividuals who gave evidence before
OL,11,Fme were very reluctant to accept it, I
OL,12,Fam satisfied from the evidence that I
OL,13,Fhave heard that a number of senior,
OL,14,Fand not-so-senior employees of the
OL,15,FPost Office knew or, at the very least
OL,16,Fshould have known, that Legacy Horizon
OL,17,Fwas capable of error.
