OL,4,Cthe teeth'
OL,6,F"Yet for all practical purposes,
OL,7,Fthroughout the lifetime of Legacy
OL,8,FHorizon, the Post Office maintained
OL,9,Fthe fiction that its data was always
OL,10,Faccurate."
OL,12,FSir Wyn made a total of 19
OL,13,Frecommendations as part of his report,
OL,14,Fincluding that the Government and the
OL,15,FPost Office should make a public
OL,16,Fannouncement about what they mean by
OL,17,F"full and fair redress".
