OL,6,FThe chairman also addressed criticism
OL,7,Fof another scheme, the Horizon
OL,8,FConvictions Redress Scheme, saying
OL,9,Fclaimants should be entitled to the
OL,10,F#600,000 fixed offer even if they
OL,11,Fsubmit their own detailed individual
OL,12,Fclaim.
OL,14,FSir Wyn urged the Government to
OL,15,Festablish a public body to devise,
OL,16,Fadminister and deliver compensation to
OL,17,Fthose wronged by authorities.
