OL,6,FThe report said the number of people
OL,7,Feligible to submit compensation claims
OL,8,Fas part of the scandal is likely to
OL,9,Frise "by at least hundreds, if not
OL,10,Fmore, over the coming months".
OL,12,FIn a statement, the Post Office said:
OL,13,F"The inquiry has brought to life the
OL,14,Fdevastating stories of those impacted
OL,15,Fby the Horizon Scandal."Their
OL,16,Fexperiences represent a shameful
OL,17,Fperiod in our history.
